ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 175 - (Saskatchewan) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 175 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes financial assistance to the province of SASKATCHEWAN with respect to the SEVERE FLOODING, that affected the Province from April 20, 2013 to August 27, 2013.
